{"word":"G4317 - προσάγω - proságō - pros-ag'-o - Bring","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">προσάγω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">proságō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pros-ag'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bring</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொண்டுவா, சேர், கிட்டிவா"},{"paragraph":"1. to lead to, bring"},{"paragraph":"2. to draw near to, approach"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a> and <a href=\"#/G71 - ἄγω - ágō - ag'-o/71\">G71</a>; to <i>lead towards</i>, that is, (transitively) to <i>conduct near</i> (<i>summon</i>, <i>present</i>), or (intransitively) to <i>approach:</i> - bring, draw near,</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3855/3855\">G3855</a>, <a href=\"#/G4254/4254\">G4254</a>, <a href=\"#/G4317/4317\">G4317</a>, <a href=\"#/G4318/4318\">G4318</a>, <a href=\"#/G72/72\">G72</a>"}]}